name: Two Door Cinema Club
wikiSummary: Two Door Cinema Club are an electropop/alternative band from Bangor and Donaghadee, Northern Ireland, United Kingdom formed in 2007. The band consists of Alex Trimble (vocals, guitar), Kevin Baird (bass, vocals) and Sam Halliday (guitar, vocals). The band does not have a permanent drummer, but they have been touring with drummer Benjamin Thompson. The band's name came about after Sam mispronounced the name of the local cinema, Tudor Cinema, and it stuck. Read more about Two Door Cinema Club on Last.fm.
